{"tid":1865851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★支爆？】中海油成疫情衝擊下首宗企業無法履約個案","createTime":"2020-02-06T11:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T11:55:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3d7299502e1c05ee845d9dfce0da80dd56ac23","tid":1865851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"外電引述兩名消息人士報道，中國海洋石油總公司已經向最少3家供應商就近期交付的液化天然氣宣佈遭遇不可抗力，成為新型冠狀病毒疫情衝擊下，首宗已知中國企業宣佈無法履約個案。<br />\n<br />\n中海油是中國最大液化天然氣進口商，佔中國總接貨能力一半。<br />\n<br />\n多名貿易商表示，正趕忙為原定送往中國的貨量尋找其他出路，導致亞洲液化天然氣現貨價格跌至紀錄新低。其中一名消息人士說，中海油宣佈遭遇不可抗力的通知，涵蓋2月及3月間液化天然氣採購。<br />\n<br />\n中海油發言人未有回應外電的報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507063-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507063-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=490f6712\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507063-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=519111f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507063-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b2cba06a975bb1d2b1e3cf8c6da96bf3904f3c0f","tid":1865851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7facde70a95ea8b5ec46720369cf663694a4c2","tid":1865851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/